### **4.3 Exchange Mechanics**

#### **Stars to Coins Conversion**
```javascript
// Conversion formula
function starsToCoins(stars) {
  const usdValue = stars / 10000; // Convert to USD
  const inrValue = usdValue * 83; // Current USD to INR rate
  const coins = (inrValue / 100) * 10000; // Convert to Coins
  return coins;
}

// Example: 50,000 Stars
// = $5 USD
// = â‚¹415 INR (at â‚¹83/$1)
// = 41,500 Coins
```

