### **4.11 Anti-Fraud Measures**

```javascript
// Prevent currency manipulation
class FraudDetection {
  checkTransaction(transaction) {
    const flags = {
      unusualAmount: transaction.amount > 1000000,
      rapidConversions: this.countRecentConversions() > 10,
      suspiciousPattern: this.detectPattern(transaction),
      newAccount: transaction.accountAge < 7 // days
    };
    
    if (Object.values(flags).some(flag => flag)) {
      return { approved: false, reason: 'Manual review required' };
    }
    
    return { approved: true };
  }
}
```

